<h3>Aims of this Design System:</h3>

<section class="boxstyle_ box1">
<ul>
<li> Consistant SO branding across all Student Opportunity services </li>
<li> Consistant user experience across all Student Opportunity services </li>
<li> Reduce custom CSS code on Student Opportunity websites</li>
<li> Increase website maintainability and accessibility</li>
<li> Responsive and mobile friendly markup by default</li>
<li> Reduce effort and duplication</li>
</ul>
</section>

